<h2>Seller account blocked</h2>

<p>A seller account has been blocked on Piessang.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Seller slug:</strong> <%= sellerSlug %></li>
  <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reasonLabel %></li>
  <% if (reasonMessage) { %>
    <li><strong>Details:</strong> <%= reasonMessage %></li>
  <% } %>
  <li><strong>Blocked at:</strong> <%= blockedAt %></li>
  <li><strong>Blocked by:</strong> <%= blockedByEmail || blockedBy %></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">
The seller account and linked product publishing access have been suspended until the issue is resolved.
</p>
